          "ruleId": "incorrect-exp",
          "level": "error",
          "message": {
            "text": "MerkleProofLib.verify(bytes32[],bytes32,bytes32) (src/utils/MerkleProofLib.sol#8-47) has bitwise-xor operator ^ instead of the exponentiation operator **: \n\t - mstore(uint256,uint256)(leafSlot_verify_asm_0 ^ 32,calldataload(uint256)(offset_verify_asm_0)) (src/utils/MerkleProofLib.sol#33)\n"
          },
